 4.4 Core [Core Finance Pty Ltd ACN 128 578 361 referred to elsewhere as ACN 073 869 897] ; or 




 4.5 Symsung [Symsung Pty Ltd ACN 079 014 243] .

On the face of my Summons for Examination: 




